      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 66,
      "message": "The problem in this class was readability (dictionary lookup isn't handy to navigate through functions) but from maintenance perspective the dictionaries are making handler functions loosely coupled. Therefore as per discussion we considered maintainability with no changes to the class.",
