      "file_path": "components/pm-subscription-handler/pmsh_service/mod/policy_response_handler.py",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 91,
      "message": "As per discussion on the trade off between readability (dictionary lookup isn't handy to navigate through functions) vs maintainability(enhancement would be easy through dictionary updates as functions are loosely coupled). So, we considered maintainability here without any changes to this function.",
